Late Pliensbachian to Late Toarcian of 
<collectingCountry box="[684,827,1963,1989]" name="Switzerland" pageId="145" pageNumber="146">Switzerland</collectingCountry>
, Toarcian of 
<collectingCountry box="[997,1077,1963,1989]" name="France" pageId="145" pageNumber="146">France</collectingCountry>
